sentences: Jack Rivers Lewis (born June 4, 1944), known professionally as Jack Wilkins, is a jazz guitarist.
In his twenties, he worked as a vibraphonist.
A copy of his first solo album, Windows (Mainstream, 1973), found its way into the hands of Buddy Rich's manager.
